    "text": "Seems like just yesterday, I diapered this little tushy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.8,
    "endTime": 18.5,
    "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, Mother, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.5,
    "endTime": 19.7,
    "text": "My tushy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.8,
    "endTime": 22.1,
    "text": "I have to work with these people, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.1,
    "endTime": 23.299000000000003,
    "text": "What are you guys doing here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.299,
    "endTime": 25.5,
    "text": "Well, you asked us to pick up Michelle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.5,
    "endTime": 27.7,
    "text": "Yes, it's 6 o'clock."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.7,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "It's only 4, Mother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 31.4,
    "text": "Oh, are we early?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.4,
    "endTime": 33.599,
    "text": "Irene, you have a camera around your neck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.599,
    "endTime": 35.099,
    "text": "You're not fooling anybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.099,
    "endTime": 36.199999999999996,
    "text": "OK, OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.2,
    "endTime": 37.900000000000006,
    "text": "We came to see Michelle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.9,
    "endTime": 40.599,
    "text": "Where's our little superstar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.599,
    "endTime": 41.799,
    "text": "Step aside, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.799,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "Make way for Miss Tanner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.799,
    "endTime": 48.7,
    "text": "Hey, Dave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.599,
    "endTime": 54.699999999999996,
    "text": "Hey, Dave, I told you you'd get a laugh with that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.7,
    "endTime": 56.299,
    "text": "No, please, no autographs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.299,
    "endTime": 58.6,
    "text": "Miss Tanner can't write."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.9,
    "endTime": 61.699999999999996,
    "text": "Look at this little cutie pie she's like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.7,
    "endTime": 64.699,
    "text": "Irene, who's that redhead I like on Gilligan's Island?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.699,
    "endTime": 66.699,
    "text": "Not Mary Ann, the movie star."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.699,
    "endTime": 67.599,
