  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.899,
    "endTime": 134.199,
    "text": "Well, see, what's happened, sir, is she's rehearsed all day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.199,
    "endTime": 135.899,
    "text": "She went through a whole bag of these."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.899,
    "endTime": 138.1,
    "text": "Oh, hey, I understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.1,
    "endTime": 139.6,
    "text": "It happens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.6,
    "endTime": 141.1,
    "text": "Dump the baby."
